    "title": "有馬記念にむけて",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『有馬記念』当日。\nナリタタイシンの居ぬ間に、\n控室には意外な来客があった。",
            "enText": "It is the day of \"Arima Kinen. While Narita \nTaishin was away, there was an unexpected \nvisitor in the waiting room.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "pathId": -2243002366997542332,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "来客――ナリタタイシンの母から\n母娘に生じているすれ違いを聞き、\n応援の花束を受け取るトレーナー。",
            "enText": "A trainer receives a bouquet of flowers from \na visitor, Narita Taishin's mother, who \ntells her of the differences between mother \nand daughter.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "pathId": 6071435731641046478,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後、戻ってきたナリタタイシンに\nファンからだと言って花束を渡すが、\nすぐに見破られてしまう。",
            "enText": "Later, she gives a bouquet of flowers \nto Narita Taishin when she returns, \nclaiming they are from a fan, but she \nis immediately recognized.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": -6069896884798546808
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 263,
                    "pathId": -70813947155240068
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2496315870293563983,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女は言う。\n母が見ていようがいまいが関係ないと。",
            "enText": "She says. She says it doesn't matter whether \nher mother is watching or not.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": 8966549288495363934
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 263,
                    "pathId": -4908083715583425189
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2457146614234709916,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――いつも通り自分のために走り、\n勝つだけだと。",
            "enText": "―She said, \"I'm going to run for \nmyself as usual and win.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
